<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<mvt:item name="html_profile" />
<head>
	<mvt:if expr="g.useDevResources EQ 1"><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list_dev" /><mvt:else><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list" /></mvt:if>
	<mvt:item name="head" param="head_tag" />
	<mvt:comment>
		Product Listing V2 staging template. Inactive only.
		Do not assign over live CTGY listing templates.
		Uses verified category_listing:products iterator from legacy category listing.
		TODO: wire facets, sorting, pagination, and product count during staging integration.
	</mvt:comment>
</head>
<body>
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_header" />
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="header" />

<main class="sd2-v2-search-page" data-v2-listing-page>
	<div class="sd2-wrap">
		<header class="sd2-v2-search-page__head">
			<nav class="sd2-v2-breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
				<a href="&mvte:urls:SFNTV2:auto;">Home</a>
				<span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
				<span>&mvte:category:name;</span>
			</nav>
			<div class="sd2-v2-search-page__title-row">
				<div>
					<p class="sd2-eyebrow">Product Listing</p>
					<h1 class="sd2-heading-lg">&mvte:category:name;</h1>
				</div>
				<p class="sd2-v2-search-page__count">&mvte:category_listing:total_prod_count; products</p>
			</div>
			<mvt:comment>TODO: register Vehicle Banner V2 in Miva Admin as readytheme contentsection('vehicle_banner') before using mvt:item composition.</mvt:comment>
		</header>

		<div class="sd2-v2-result-tools">
			<div class="sd2-v2-chips" data-v2-filter-chips><span class="sd2-v2-chip">&mvte:category:name;</span></div>
			<button class="sd2-v2-filter-trigger" type="button" data-v2-filter-open aria-controls="sd2-v2-listing-filter-sheet" aria-expanded="false">Filters</button>
			<form class="sd2-v2-sort" method="get" action="&mvte:urls:_self:auto_noparams;">
				<mvt:if expr="tolower( l.settings:category_listing:mode ) EQ 'ctgy' AND toupper( g.Screen ) NE 'CTGY'">
					<input type="hidden" name="Category_Code" value="&mvte:global:Category_Code;" />
				<mvt:elseif expr="tolower( l.settings:category_listing:mode ) EQ 'relp' AND toupper( g.Screen ) NE 'PROD'">
					<input type="hidden" name="Product_Code" value="&mvte:global:Product_Code;" />
				</mvt:if>
				<mvt:item name="urls" param="hidden_params:_self:auto" />
				<input type="hidden" name="Search" value="&mvte:global:Search;" />
				<input type="hidden" name="Per_Page" value="&mvte:global:Per_Page;" />
				<mvt:foreach iterator="facet" array="facets:applied_facets">
					<mvt:foreach iterator="facet_value" array="facet:input_values">
						<input type="hidden" name="&mvte:facet:code;" value="&mvte:facet_value;" />
					</mvt:foreach>
				</mvt:foreach>
				<label class="sd2-label" for="sd2-v2-listing-sort">Sort</label>
				<select class="sd2-field" id="sd2-v2-listing-sort" name="Sort_By" onchange="this.form.submit();">
					<mvt:if expr="ISNULL g.Sort_By">
						<option value="disp_order" selected="selected">Recommended</option>
					<mvt:else>
						<option value="disp_order">Recommended</option>
					</mvt:if>
					<mvt:if expr="g.Sort_By EQ 'bestsellers'">
						<option value="bestsellers" selected="selected">Best Selling</option>
					<mvt:else>
						<option value="bestsellers">Best Selling</option>
					</mvt:if>
					<mvt:if expr="g.Sort_By EQ 'price_asc'">
						<option value="price_asc" selected="selected">Price: Low to High</option>
					<mvt:else>
						<option value="price_asc">Price: Low to High</option>
					</mvt:if>
					<mvt:if expr="g.Sort_By EQ 'price_desc'">
						<option value="price_desc" selected="selected">Price: High to Low</option>
					<mvt:else>
						<option value="price_desc">Price: High to Low</option>
					</mvt:if>
					<mvt:if expr="g.Sort_By EQ 'newest'">
						<option value="newest" selected="selected">Newest Items</option>
					<mvt:else>
						<option value="newest">Newest Items</option>
					</mvt:if>
				</select>
			</form>
		</div>

		<section class="sd2-v2-search-page__layout" aria-label="Category products">
			<aside class="sd2-v2-filter-rail" aria-label="Filters">
				<mvt:comment>TODO: wire native Miva facets into the existing Filter Rail component.</mvt:comment>
				<section class="sd2-v2-filter-group is-open">
					<button class="sd2-v2-filter-group__head" type="button" aria-expanded="true">Category <span aria-hidden="true">+</span></button>
					<div class="sd2-v2-filter-group__body">
						<label class="sd2-v2-filter-opt"><input type="checkbox" disabled> [Placeholder] Miva facet</label>
					</div>
				</section>
			</aside>

			<div class="sd2-v2-pgrid-wrap">
				<div class="sd2-v2-pgrid" data-v2-product-grid>
					<mvt:comment>
						Verified legacy pattern: category listings render inline product cards
						inside category_listing:products (see ctgy-category_listing.mvt). No file
						include is available. Add-to-cart form fields, hidden Offset/facet params,
						and the AddToBasketE button item are reused verbatim from that legacy file
						to preserve basket/facet/offset business logic exactly.
					</mvt:comment>
					<mvt:foreach iterator="product" array="category_listing:products">
						<article class="sd2-card sd2-v2-product-card">
							<a class="sd2-v2-product-card__media" href="&mvte:urls:PRODV2:auto;?Product_Code=&mvta:product:code;" data-mm-linktype="product-list-link">
								<mvt:if expr="NOT ISNULL l.settings:product:thumbnail">
									<img src="&mvte:product:thumbnail;" alt="&mvte:product:name;" loading="lazy">
								<mvt:else>
									<img src="graphics/00000001/placeholder.png" alt="" loading="lazy">
								</mvt:if>
								<mvt:if expr="l.settings:product:inv_level EQ 'out'">
									<span class="sd2-v2-product-card__flag">Out of Stock</span>
								</mvt:if>
							</a>
							<div class="sd2-v2-product-card__body">
								<p class="sd2-v2-product-card__platform">SKU &mvte:product:code;</p>
								<h3 class="sd2-v2-product-card__title"><a href="&mvte:urls:PRODV2:auto;?Product_Code=&mvta:product:code;" data-mm-linktype="product-list-link">&mvte:product:name;</a></h3>
								<p class="sd2-v2-product-card__note" data-v2-fitment-copy>No vehicle selected. Confirm fitment in Garage.</p>
								<mvt:if expr="l.settings:product:inv_active">
									<p class="sd2-v2-product-card__inv">&mvt:product:inv_long;</p>
								</mvt:if>
								<div class="sd2-v2-product-card__foot">
									<span class="sd2-v2-product-card__price">
										<mvt:if expr="l.settings:product:base_price GT l.settings:product:price">
											<s>&mvt:product:formatted_base_price;</s>
										</mvt:if>
										&mvt:product:formatted_price;
									</span>
									<a class="sd2-v2-product-card__link" href="&mvte:urls:PRODV2:auto;?Product_Code=&mvta:product:code;" data-mm-linktype="product-list-link">View</a>
								</div>
								<mvt:if expr="l.settings:product:inv_level NE 'out'">
									<form class="sd2-v2-product-card__cart-form" method="post" action="&mvte:urls:BASK:rr;">
										<input type="hidden" name="Old_Screen" value="&mvte:global:Screen;" />
										<input type="hidden" name="Old_Search" value="&mvte:global:Search;" />
										<input type="hidden" name="Action" value="ADPR" />
										<input type="hidden" name="Quantity" value="1" />
										<input type="hidden" name="Attributes" value="Yes" />
										<input type="hidden" name="Product_Code" value="&mvte:product:code;" />
										<input type="hidden" name="Current_Product_Code" value="&mvte:global:Product_Code;" />
										<input type="hidden" name="Category_Code" value="&mvte:global:Category_Code;" />
										<input type="hidden" name="Offset" value="&mvte:global:CatListingOffset;" />
										<input type="hidden" name="AllOffset" value="&mvte:global:AllOffset;" />
										<input type="hidden" name="CatListingOffset" value="&mvte:global:CatListingOffset;" />
										<input type="hidden" name="RelatedOffset" value="&mvte:global:RelatedOffset;" />
										<input type="hidden" name="SearchOffset" value="&mvte:global:SearchOffset;" />
										<mvt:foreach iterator="facet" array="facets:applied_facets">
											<mvt:foreach iterator="facet_value" array="facet:input_values">
												<input type="hidden" name="&mvte:facet:code;" value="&mvte:facet_value;" />
											</mvt:foreach>
										</mvt:foreach>
										<mvt:item name="buttons" param="AddToBasketE" />
									</form>
								</mvt:if>
							</div>
						</article>
					</mvt:foreach>
					<mvt:if expr="miva_array_elements(l.settings:category_listing:products) EQ 0">
						<section class="sd2-v2-empty-state" aria-label="No products in this category">
							<h2>No products currently available</h2>
							<p>This category has no products matching the current filters.</p>
						</section>
					</mvt:if>
				</div>
				<mvt:if expr="l.settings:category_listing:page_links:last_page GT 1">
					<nav class="sd2-v2-pagination" aria-label="Pagination">
						<mvt:if expr="l.settings:category_listing:page_links:current_page NE 1">
							<a class="sd2-v2-pagination__prev" href="&mvte:urls:_self:auto_sep;&mvte:category_listing:page_links:prev_link_params;">Previous</a>
						<mvt:else>
							<span class="sd2-v2-pagination__prev is-disabled">Previous</span>
						</mvt:if>
						<span class="sd2-v2-pagination__pages">
							<mvt:if expr="NOT l.settings:category_listing:page_links:contains_first">
								<a class="sd2-v2-pagination__link" href="&mvte:urls:_self:auto_sep;&mvte:category_listing:page_links:first_link_params;">1</a>
								<span aria-hidden="true">&hellip;</span>
							</mvt:if>
							<mvt:foreach iterator="pages" array="category_listing:page_links:pages">
								<mvt:if expr="l.settings:category_listing:page_links:current_page EQ l.settings:pages:page_num">
									<span class="sd2-v2-pagination__link is-current">&mvte:pages:page_num;</span>
								<mvt:else>
									<a class="sd2-v2-pagination__link" href="&mvte:urls:_self:auto_sep;&mvte:pages:link_params;">&mvte:pages:page_num;</a>
								</mvt:if>
							</mvt:foreach>
							<mvt:if expr="NOT l.settings:category_listing:page_links:contains_last">
								<span aria-hidden="true">&hellip;</span>
								<a class="sd2-v2-pagination__link" href="&mvte:urls:_self:auto_sep;&mvte:category_listing:page_links:last_link_params;">&mvte:category_listing:page_links:last_page;</a>
							</mvt:if>
						</span>
						<mvt:if expr="l.settings:category_listing:page_links:current_page NE l.settings:category_listing:page_links:last_page">
							<a class="sd2-v2-pagination__next" href="&mvte:urls:_self:auto_sep;&mvte:category_listing:page_links:next_link_params;">Next</a>
						<mvt:else>
							<span class="sd2-v2-pagination__next is-disabled">Next</span>
						</mvt:if>
					</nav>
				</mvt:if>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>

	<div class="sd2-v2-filter-sheet-scrim" data-v2-filter-close hidden></div>
	<aside class="sd2-v2-filter-sheet" id="sd2-v2-listing-filter-sheet" aria-label="Mobile filters" aria-hidden="true" data-v2-filter-sheet>
		<header class="sd2-v2-filter-sheet__head">
			<h2>Filters</h2>
			<button class="sd2-icon-btn" type="button" data-v2-filter-close aria-label="Close filters">x</button>
		</header>
		<div class="sd2-v2-filter-sheet__body">
			<mvt:comment>TODO: mirror confirmed Miva facets from the filter rail.</mvt:comment>
			<section class="sd2-v2-filter-group is-open">
				<button class="sd2-v2-filter-group__head" type="button" aria-expanded="true">Category <span aria-hidden="true">+</span></button>
				<div class="sd2-v2-filter-group__body">
					<label class="sd2-v2-filter-opt"><input type="checkbox" disabled> [Placeholder] Miva facet</label>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
		<footer class="sd2-v2-filter-sheet__foot">
			<button class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--primary sd2-btn--wide" type="button" data-v2-filter-close>View Results</button>
		</footer>
	</aside>
</main>

	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="footer" />
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_footer" />
</body>
</html>
